➜涉案20亿！日照警方成功破获特大暴力虚开增值税专用发票案
http://www.sohu.com/a/415201462_99909796	38679
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200827/d2940ee0677a464d901f416e61689950.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200827/82f8c866fe0d4efaac1a1c585316d5f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200827/19d9a658b0584485a5c403da01efa504.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200827/426831a411aa49d2aa3abad03d8c9d0f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
